  <html xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_1_0.xsd"
   xmlns:p="tapestry:parameter"  xmlns:tx="tapestry-library:tapx">
    <head>
        <title>YUI Rich Test Editor demo</title>
  

    </head>
     

    <body>
        <h1>YUI Rich Test editor Demo</h1>  
    A demo on the <a href="${message:tapxGitHomePage}">Tapx YUI RichTextEditor component </a>. 
     
    The source code is
<a href="#" t:type="PageLink" t:page="sci/richTextEditorDemoSource"
	target="_blank">here</a>. 
<br />

      <h2>Input Form</h2>
    <t:form clientValidation="false">

        <t:errors/>
        <tx:richtexteditor t:id="richText" width="800" height="400" validate="required"/>

        <br/>

        <input type="submit" value="Submit"/>
    </t:form>
      
  <h2>Output</h2>

  <div id="output">
    <t:outputraw value="richText"/>
  </div>

 </body>
</html>